{"tid":1682864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想發起一個全民退卡行動","createTime":"2019-10-30T10:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T10:32:34.000Z","uid":308525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9970fed7fe605c08b6d1b9284b706e4491a15f14","tid":1682864,"uid":308525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵</span>嘅八達通你用100蚊佢賺兩蚊 仲要每張卡有50蚊按金係黨鐵手上 我當全香港200萬個手足都有張卡 姐係夾夾埋埋有一億按金係黨鐵手上 唔好比佢攞大家嘅錢去投資然後賺到傻好無？唔通你班香港人嬲完黨鐵啦咩？咁快唔記得721同831發生咩事？點解每日搭車/買嘢都仲會聽到嘟嘟聲？我正式宣佈由依家開始要罷用八達通呢張閪卡！屌你罷用應該都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為免大家貪方便用左張卡 大家一齊退卡啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽到未啊香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日都係全民退卡日啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">快 啲 攞 張 閪 卡 去 退 啊</span>[/size=5]"},{"pid":"65fc8b9f7482f81fc7105d0110799dbebfb3561f","tid":1682864,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"營業模式:  <br />\n<br />\n<strong>根據手足經濟能力的不同</strong>:   <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟能力充裕</span> ----&gt; 以 <strong>正常價格</strong> 購買貨品 ----&gt; 令店鋪能持續經營 ----&gt; 擴充并聘請義士 + 利潤支持長期抗爭   <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">手足有需要幫手</span> ----&gt; 利用優惠碼以 <strong>成本價</strong> 購買貨品(注1) ----&gt; 手足減輕生活成本 ----&gt; 可支配收入增加 <br />\n<br />\n[榮光歸港人互助計劃] 讓有需要既手足都能以成本價買野 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681328</a> <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea23193e0dc4ba3cbf0c7b3b0c5e3454c0166a02","tid":1682864,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:32:34.000Z","msg"